<subSubSection pageId="30" pageNumber="423" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="30.[2013,2610,2300,2727]" pageId="30" pageNumber="423">
<taxonomicName box="[2015,2204,2423,2452]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="sonomae">Sorex sonomae</taxonomicName>
is in the 
<taxonomicName box="[2360,2508,2423,2452]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="sonomae">S. sonomae</taxonomicName>
group along with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Coues" authorityYear="1877" box="[2169,2311,2458,2491]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="pacificus">S. pacificus</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1895" box="[2379,2484,2458,2491]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bairdi">S. bairdi</taxonomicName>
and sub- genus Otisorex. The 
<taxonomicName box="[2294,2435,2501,2530]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="sonomae">S. sonomae</taxonomicName>
group 1s sister to the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1890" box="[2156,2324,2537,2570]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="monticolus">S. monticolus</taxonomicName>
group and includes northern populations of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1890" box="[2377,2549,2576,2609]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="monticolus">S. monticolus</taxonomicName>
, sister to 
<taxonomicName box="[2117,2265,2615,2648]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="sonomae">S. sonomae</taxonomicName>
. Continued taxonomic revision is needed to resolve paraphyly of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1890" box="[2016,2186,2694,2727]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="monticolus">S. monticolus</taxonomicName>
with respect to the S. 
<taxonomicName box="[2501,2608,2694,2727]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="sonomae">sonomae</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="30.[1403,2610,2735,3477]" pageId="30" pageNumber="423">
group and exact placement of 
<taxonomicName box="[1835,1975,2735,2768]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="sonomae">S. sonomae</taxonomicName>
, which is either sister to the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="J. Richardson" authorityYear="1828" box="[2374,2515,2735,2768]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="palustris">S. palustris</taxonomicName>
group and the Coastal 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1890" box="[1630,1797,2774,2807]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="monticolus">S. monticolus</taxonomicName>
+ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Coues" authorityYear="1877" box="[1829,1977,2774,2807]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="pacificus">S. pacificus</taxonomicName>
/ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1895" box="[1991,2098,2774,2807]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bairdi">S. bairdi</taxonomicName>
clade, or closer to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Coues" authorityYear="1877" box="[2361,2503,2774,2807]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="pacificus">S. pacificus</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1895" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="bairdi">S. bairdi</taxonomicName>
, and the Coastal 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1890" box="[1675,1843,2814,2847]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="30" pageNumber="423" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="monticolus">S. monticolus</taxonomicName>
. Two subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
